{"tid":2340231,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【12港人家屬譴責中國當局擬秘密審訊12人】","createTime":"2020-12-25T09:41:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-25T15:25:47.000Z","uid":240362,"like":15,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"1c082651379b3e547be6c66f8f33701e1959af6e","tid":2340231,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:41:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-0/p526x296/131998992_227257352448028_384536815743992980_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;ccb=2&amp;_nc_sid=8bfeb9&amp;_nc_ohc=L-Kqg5b_HkwAX-ZAr1j&amp;_nc_oc=AQmeY7_E7Mhrhqd1b-rQAGGp74yQk874Pp8sGGiRNmc3OarliWIPiYUyQCdVf5JarlY&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkt1-2.xx&amp;tp=6&amp;oh=642fd1b587387b04ad9938d491ba4a01&amp;oe=600B6457\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkt1-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-0%2Fp526x296%2F131998992_227257352448028_384536815743992980_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26ccb%3D2%26_nc_sid%3D8bfeb9%26_nc_ohc%3DL-Kqg5b_HkwAX-ZAr1j%26_nc_oc%3DAQmeY7_E7Mhrhqd1b-rQAGGp74yQk874Pp8sGGiRNmc3OarliWIPiYUyQCdVf5JarlY%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkt1-2.xx%26tp%3D6%26oh%3D642fd1b587387b04ad9938d491ba4a01%26oe%3D600B6457&h=7a10a1f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n12港人被秘密關押超過四個月，當中7人家屬今日突然收到由中國當局指派的「官派律師」通知，指其中10人將於12月28日星期一下午2時30分，以視像方式於深圳市鹽田區人民法院受審。另外2名於被捕時未滿18歲的港人，則會由檢察院聽證會處理，日期未知。<br />\n<br />\n12港人中，10人須面對審訊，但目前僅7人的家屬收到開庭通知。鹽田法院回覆傳媒查詢時明言，12港人案件屬於「秘密案件」，將不允許公眾人士、記者等人旁聽，僅著家屬自行聯絡負責審訊的法官詢問能否旁聽。而在鹽田法院公佈的庭審直播時間表，亦未有列出10位港人的審訊。<br />\n<br />\n由於法院在審訊前3日才發出通知，當中包括公眾假期，家屬已無法趕及親自到法庭旁聽。對於中國當局將秘密審訊12港人，家屬予以強烈譴責 &mdash; 此做法完全漠視基本人權價值，亦違背中國對外宣傳之「陽光司法」原則。<br />\n<br />\n家屬在此向中國當局要求：<br />\n&bull;  全程網絡視像直播庭審；<br />\n&bull;  向家屬及全港公眾公開12港人案件審訊詳情，包括兩位未成年人進行聽證的日期、庭審形式及法官資料等；<br />\n&bull;  公開庭審，讓家屬代表、家屬委託律師、香港及國際媒體、各國外交使節人員能到場旁聽；<br />\n&bull;  要求當局在審訊後對外公布判決書；及<br />\n&bull;  承諾若12港人最終被判監禁，家屬可盡快探望。<br />\n另要求香港政府：<br />\n&bull;  派員旁聽案件，確保12港人作為香港公民的權利得到保障。<br />\n<br />\n12港人家屬<br />\n2020年12月25日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/save12hkyouths/posts/227257632448000\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsave12hkyouths%2Fposts%2F227257632448000&d=E3iW9F3hP8nhDbvOoRyiQBjXlokmAnOoGQHL1SEg040%3D&h=e38d4149\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/save12hkyouths/posts/227257632448000</a>"},{"pid":"7b29adb0cfd65d7171aa28771d112d704aff1877","tid":2340231,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea34ef8f51cab8b9496649fc74139c1b5f4062c","tid":2340231,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7b29adb0cfd65d7171aa28771d112d704aff1877","tid":2340231,"uid":232157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:43:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:44:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"301f1ea05486b7de5e7f47ecb0c9f058e08334e3","tid":2340231,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:46:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"81ad7b06a5c75d296963b15397b7df2c7fd6e029","tid":2340231,"uid":279333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-25T09:46:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pi